Kondo your financial house
--------------------------

Kakeibo (or kakebo) was created by Japanese journalist Hani
Motoko in 1904 as a household accounting system, and it blends
thoughtful goal-setting with bookkeeping. The results go beyond=20
( https://t.dripemail2.com/c/eyJhY2NvdW50X2lkIjoiNDMxMTg3MCIsImRlbGl2ZXJ5X2=
