ing.

The Japanese believe that tidiness in one=E2=80=99s finances is as
important as tidiness in one=E2=80=99s house =E2=80=94 and indeed for them,=
 the
act of thinking mindfully about where one=E2=80=99s money goes is in
itself a recipe for calm and well-being.

To get started, all you need is to know is how much money you
