<blockquote style=3D"background-color: #fafafa; color: #666; font-style: it=
alic; margin-left: 0; padding: 20px 30px;">
<p style=3D"color: #333;">To ride out the storm, professionals of all gener=
ations appear to be turning to =E2=80=9Cportfolio careers=E2=80=9D to earn =
their living through a mix of contracted freelance jobs, consulting gigs, s=
hort-term projects, board membership, and other engagements that allow them=
 to apply their expertise under flexible conditions.</p>
</blockquote>

<p style=3D"color: #333;">Given that Generation X is already at a point whe=
re ageist layoffs arise, job dissatisfaction is high, and disruptive automa=
tion technologies are coming even faster due to COVID-19, we may <a href=3D=
"https://t.dripemail2.com/c/eyJhY2NvdW50X2lkIjoiNDMxMTg3MCIsImRlbGl2ZXJ5X2l=
kIjoidzRoZTlvMWQzMjM2ZzRwb253YTIiLCJ1cmwiOiJodHRwczovL3d3dy5mYXN0Y29tcGFueS=
