ner noreferrer" target=3D"_blank" style=3D"color: #be8100;">lead the charge=
</a> away from traditional employment arrangements:</p>

<blockquote style=3D"background-color: #fafafa; color: #666; font-style: it=
alic; margin-left: 0; padding: 20px 30px;">
<p style=3D"color: #333;">With stronger levels of dissatisfaction building =
before COVID-19, it is safe to assume that this crisis may push Gen-Xers, i=
n particular, to steer their careers in a new direction. According to data =
from BMO Wealth Management, 50% of Gen-Xers who have portfolio careers cite=
 =E2=80=9Chaving autonomy and control=E2=80=9D as a top motivator for self-=
employment=E2=80=94the highest of all generations.</p>
</blockquote>

<p style=3D"color: #333;">Another way to think about a =E2=80=9Cportfolio c=
areer=E2=80=9D is the <em>personal enterprise</em>. The term was coined in =
the book <a href=3D"https://t.dripemail2.com/c/eyJhY2NvdW50X2lkIjoiNDMxMTg3=
MCIsImRlbGl2ZXJ5X2lkIjoidzRoZTlvMWQzMjM2ZzRwb253YTIiLCJ1cmwiOiJodHRwczovL2F=
