get=3D"_blank" style=3D"color: #be8100;">Unscaled</a> by Hemant Taneja, and=
 he means that the key to navigating the coming economy is to live an <em>e=
ntrepreneurial life</em>.</p>

<p style=3D"color: #333;">His use of =E2=80=9Centrepreneurial=E2=80=9D is a=
 bit different than you may be thinking. Taneja is a venture capitalist who=
 sees most full-time jobs disappearing (even if the pandemic didn=E2=80=99t=
 happen), replaced by just-in-time contractual talent that operates via enh=
anced technology.</p>

<p style=3D"color: #333;">Instead of a crafting a resume to land a single e=
mployer, Taneja sees a mix of long-term contracts, freelance projects, side=
 hustles, and entrepreneurial products that you develop and market with the=
 aid of the AI and automation that once threatened to replace you.</p>

<p style=3D"color: #333;">Will this be a challenging shift for more job-ori=
ented people? Yes, but I=E2=80=99m afraid everyone needs to <a href=3D"http=
